{{#if stats}}
### Bundle Impact Report 📈

{{#each stats}}

<details>
<summary>{{@key}} ({{ join (filesize this.diff.gzip 2 true) (filesize this.stat.[0].gzip) }} ) {{impact this.diff.gzip 5 "🟢 Near-Zero Impact" 100 "🟡 Low Impact" 200 "🟠 Medium Impact" 500 "🔴 High Impact" "🟥 Extreme Impact"}}</summary>

{{#each this.stat}}
- {{ tooltip (or (bold this.label) this.tag "- - -") (date this.date) }} ({{ this.sha }}) - **{{ filesize gzip }}** ({{join (filesize diff.size 2 true) (filesize size) (percent compressed)}})
{{else}}
  **No data collected**
{{/each}}

{{#if graph}}
#### Graph 📊

<pre>
{{ graph }}
</pre>
{{/if}}
</details>
{{/each}}
{{/if}}
